Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:00.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(302,462)}追寻那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:06.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(302,462)}我会诚实地面对自己所有的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:10.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(302,462)}风和星空仍记着那时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:19.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(302,462)}当我们相互拥抱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我的梦想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为偶像明星不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小兔你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是小卫啰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往回看我感觉好遥远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该是美奈子我实现自己梦想的时候了
